<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965">  content</span><span style="--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666">:</span><span style="--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D"> My Custom Content</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666">---</span></span></code></pre>
</div><p>支持的配置项请参考：<a href="https://zhensherlock.github.io/watermark-js-plus/zh/config/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">watermark-js-plus</a></p>
